{"chunk": "Management is responsible for Management's Review.
Our opinion on the Financial Statements does
not cover Management's Review, and we do not express
any form of assurance conclusion thereon.
In connection with our audit of the Financial
Statements, our responsibility is to read Management's
Review and, in doing so, consider whether
Management's Review is materially inconsistent with the
Financial Statements or our knowledge obtained during
the audit, or otherwise appears to be materially
misstated.", "context": "This chunk is from the "Statement on the Management's review" section of the independent auditor's report for the financial statements of Bruhn Newtech A/S."}
